In a #pot{} combine @salted butter{1/2 cup}, @cocoa powder{1/3 cup}, @granulated sugar{1 3/4 cup}, and @milk{1/2 cup}.

Stir frequently and cook until it reaches a full boil. Let it boil for about a minute without stirring.

Remove from heat and add @vanilla{1 tsp}, @peanut butter{2/3 cup}, and @quick oats{3 cups}.

Place dollops on a #baking sheet{} and let set in the refrigerator or freezer.

Once set, enjoy!
